Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.77,0:00:03.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:06.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The S Class Wizard Advancement \NExam was held on Tenroujima.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:12.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up participating as Cana's partner \Nafter she confessed something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:15.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But during the exam Zeref appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.49,0:00:17.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Grimoire Heart came to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.73,0:00:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is going to happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:56.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana acquired one of the 3 Grand \NSpells of the guild, Fairy Glitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't enough to \Nstand up to the magic power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:02.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,of the second-in-command of \NGrimoire Heart, Bluenote.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:05.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana was facing a truly dire situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:12.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's when Cana's \Nfather, Gildarts, returned!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:20.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy... He's Gildarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.76,0:02:34.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:45.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenrou Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:11.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Gildarts this angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:13.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The tension in the air is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:15.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:23.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ground's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...turned upside down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.25,0:03:52.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How much magic power do \Nthe both of them have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Carla...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:56.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I didn't exactly cover for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:04.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pushed back? Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't come off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:16.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think maybe we should get \Naway from here, like he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:18.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:27.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We would just get in Gildarts's way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:42.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:55.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:09.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a very important exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:15.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It meant much more to the \Nkids than the adults knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:21.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The determination of those kids \Nto step out into tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.83,0:05:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You trampled all over it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! I wanna see how the fight ends up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, joining up with \Neveryone else comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:35.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:38.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we go to the camp, \Neveryone might be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:41.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to regroup and prepare, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:46.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Mest-san... I mean, Dranbalt-san \Nwill surely help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.63,0:05:47.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:51.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cana, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:06:01.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Fairy Tail's base camp, \Nwhere Natsu's group is heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:06.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wounded members are carried here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:12.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am one of the 7 Kin \Nof Purgatory, Rustyrose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:17.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll devour every last Fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:20.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna, we're gonna protect \Neveryone back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:23.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood! I'm not going to let \Nhim lay a finger on Mira-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:27.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only maintain my battle \Nform for a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to finish this quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Women, a cat, and the wounded?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:39.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, this doesn't seem like it'll \Nbe a particularly dramatic event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:40.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:44.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's the injured, \NI will not hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will crush you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just picking on the weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:51.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The strongest Dark Guild, my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel any shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how you do things, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:07:01.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We will sacrifice as many people as \Nit takes to create our ideal world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, no weaklings \Nare meant to survive there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will never create \Nan ideal world that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:13.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! We learned that first-hand in Edolas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then use your powers and try to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:21.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should try to shake my \Nfragment much, much more! {again, he uses "fragment" as a metaphor for "heart"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cry! Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:34.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those voices will be your requiem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:41.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried! Bickslow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You came back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We noticed the signal flare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:54.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We came back together with Gildarts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:56.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts is back, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:02.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! My Ark of Embodiment isn't going to \Nhave trouble with a few more weaklings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:08.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn the whole bunch of you \Ninto tragic memorial stardust!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.31,0:08:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We never planned on fighting \Nyou fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:15.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us together will \Nwipe you out completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:19.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,By hurting Ever and our \Ncomrades, you have sinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:21.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rules do not apply to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Baryon Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In my left hand dwells a shield \Nof gold that defends against all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:43.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Within my feet dwell Pegasus's wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can beat \Nthe power of imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:51.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you can beat my infinite power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.82,0:08:55.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacred Guardian Beast, Gale Belfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:59.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mow them all down! Make my fragment shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:02.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What... is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.63,0:09:06.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Summoning magic... Wait, I can \Nsense a different kind of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried! Bickslow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:11.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to remind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seith Magic! Human Possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Écriture of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now {\i1}that's{\i0} the Raijinshuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.38,0:09:41.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how they are when \Nthey fight seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:48.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no path to forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:55.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My fragment... It fears?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:10:00.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant tree, which makes \Nits roots on Tenroujima...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:05.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There at its roots, the two \Nstrong warriors finally meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:07.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza and Azuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:10.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You finished off Wendy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.41,0:10:12.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And not just that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:18.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of your comrades should be getting \Ndestroyed by my allies right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:22.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have Natsu and Mirajane here as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:23.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you couldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:26.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about this \Nwizard you call Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:38.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the Demon Mirajane I defeated myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:42.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you think I am lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:47.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will find out for myself \Nwith my own two eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:11:01.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Mirajane, and now \NTitania, Erza Scarlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:06.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How lucky I am to destroy both myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:17.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Further inside the island, Ultear met \NGray and told him something shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to meet me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:23.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been searching for you all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:34.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the most loved of Ul's \Nstudents, and I am Ul's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.35,0:11:37.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost like little \Nbrother and big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:41.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! B-Brother and s-sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:43.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're my sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:46.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it's kind of like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:49.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I have no reason to hate you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:53.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to buy this all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:55.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're our enemy, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:12:00.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I'm a member \Nof Grimoire Heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:04.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But even though we stand against each other, \NI'm sure that we can speak heart to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.35,0:12:09.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us follow the path \NUl set out for us, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:21.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle on Tenroujima \Nheaded toward its conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We all believed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:29.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We believed we'd be victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.54,0:12:45.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we believed. {check out the newspaper for a single frame... It has the date}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear... Catastrophe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:11.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My fragment... It fears?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:27.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fear causes my power... my \Nimagination to build up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:33.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go forth, spirits of Prettia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Devour the Fairies' souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Here come more weird things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:41.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're clinging to my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he mean his magic can turn \Nanything he imagines into reality?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How in the world can you fight against that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:57.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy uses some creepy magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried and Bickslow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:05.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember now. You two are \Npart of the Raijinshuu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:08.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those groupies of Master Makarov's grandson,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,who was expelled for trying and \Nfailing to take control of the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:16.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was his name again? \NOh yeah, Laxus, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:18.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:25.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A contemptible scoundrel like you \Nhas no right to utter Laxus' name!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:31.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, this guy can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:50.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,BLEVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:03.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Venus Photon Slicer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:17.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for \Nsomeone strong like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.14,0:15:19.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear of your bravery quite often.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:27.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you and I may be of the same \Nbreed, where the fight is everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:31.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only searching for those \Nwho are truly strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I cannot agree with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not search out those who are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.45,0:15:43.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:46.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You would never have obtained \Nsuch strength unless you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:54.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I have the power to protect \Nmy friends, that's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:59.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could trade for that power, \NI wouldn't care how weak I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:04.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... that's contradictory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:07.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:10.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could fight you fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.81,0:16:12.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:14.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean that time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:18.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:25.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic is of the forest. Tree magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Lost Magic, Great Tree Ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My explosions are caused by using the magic \Nof the great land to compress tree roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:44.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the true power of this magic
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is to root into the ground and to control \Nthe magic power residing in the great land.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Control the magic of the land?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:57.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There was but one reason for me to arrive \Non this island before everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:00.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so I could prepare to take \Ncontrol over this island's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:06.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:12.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not what I would have wished for, \Nbut I cannot disobey a direct order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:15.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What have you done, you fiend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:31.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the... The Tenrou Tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:35.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,T-The island! The island is crumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:40.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that giant tree that's crumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:46.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should have forced \Nthem to evacuate after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:55.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:03.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you stay safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:08.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:11.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Carla, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:16.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to hurry back to the camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:25.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:30.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like all my energy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:47.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuma, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All my power is disappearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:58.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried, Bickslow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:16.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing Stream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The flow has reversed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:21.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have the last laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bring out any of my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:35.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... I can't summon any power...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:42.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.57,0:19:52.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, old man... You gave Azuma \Nsome strange orders, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:05.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts. Makarov... You have a fine \Nchess piece in your possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:11.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To think someone else could \Nstop Bluenote other than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.22,0:20:17.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It did take quite some time, but have you \Ntaken control over the magic of Tenroujima?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:26.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, Fairy Tail has lost even \Nits slightest chance of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:39.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master Hades knows the \Npower of this island well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.53,0:20:40.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:46.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The giant tree growing in its \Ncenter, the Tenrou Tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.21,0:20:51.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It provides divine protection to \Nthose with the Fairy Tail mark,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:54.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and protects them from \Ndying while on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:57.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a special ability \Nto amplify magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:01.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why the master has \Nthe exam on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you destroyed the Tenrou Tree?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:12.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That nullified the divine \Nprotection on your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:18.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I am stealing away the magic \Npower of every Fairy Tail wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:33.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an elegant visual, \Nfitting for all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:39.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.25,0:21:43.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.38,0:21:47.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail has surely been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:59.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I control the magic of the \Nisland, I have left you as you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:03.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Titania...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:05.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are at death's \Ndoor around the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:08.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the only one who can save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.15,0:22:13.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just see how great this power is \Nthat you have to protect your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.63,0:23:59.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But man, the tree in the middle \Nof this island is seriously big.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:00.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of tree is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:01.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:03.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the Tenrou Tree, but \NI've never heard of that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.88,0:24:05.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Its name sounds strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.90,0:24:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.75,0:24:09.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think trees are \N"strong" or "weak", really.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.04,0:24:12.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... I bet if I punched it, \Nit'd start moving or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.16,0:24:13.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't even think about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.01,0:24:16.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Erza vs. Azuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:20.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And anyway, if a big tree like this \Nmoved, you'd be squished flat, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.82,0:24:22.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like a tree can move around, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who brought it up!
